NOTE ON BUILD OUTPUTS

This license covers the *build scripts and configuration* in this repository.
The artifacts they produce are builds of FFmpeg (https://ffmpeg.org), which is
licensed under the LGPL v2.1+. These builds are configured WITHOUT --enable-gpl
and WITHOUT --enable-nonfree, and contain no GPL components (no libx264 /
libx265), so the produced libraries are LGPL-licensed. Distributing software
that links them must comply with the LGPL (e.g. permit relinking). See the
FFmpeg LICENSE and the per-release manifest for the exact components built.
